<div class="modal-header">
  <h5 class="modal-title" id="verifyLabel">Verifying <%= character.name %></h5>
  <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
</div>
<div class="modal-body">
  <p>
    XIVAuth did not detect your verification code on your character page. Since this can be caused by lag on Square
    Enix's side, we'll be trying again in about a couple of minutes.
  </p>
  <p>
    To ensure successful verification, please ensure the below code is located on <%= character.name %>'s
    <%= link_to "Lodestone profile", registration.lodestone_url, target: "_blank", rel: 'noreferrer noopener' %>, and
    appears exactly as it does below.
  </p>
  <div class="input-group mb-3" data-controller="utilities--copy-code">
    <input type="text" data-utilities--copy-code-target="source" readonly class="form-control text-center font-monospace"
           value="<%= registration.verification_key %>" aria-label="Verification code">
    <button class="btn btn-outline-secondary" type="button" data-action="utilities--copy-code#copy" data-utilities--copy-code-target="button">
      <i class="bi bi-clipboard"></i> Copy
    </button>
  </div>
  <p>
    This dialog will automatically update after the next attempt. You may also close this dialog at any time.
  </p>
</div>
<div class="modal-footer">
  <div class="me-auto">
    <div class="text-secondary very-small align-middle">
      Job ID: <span class="font-monospace"><%= job.job_id %></span><br/>
      Attempt <%= job.executions + 1 %> of <%= job.class::MAX_RETRY_ATTEMPTS %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">Got it.</button>
</div>